{"tid":706903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"代課導師展示煙草物分享吸大麻經驗　校方稱跟進","createTime":"2018-06-18T09:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T12:16:23.000Z","uid":122,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"191d556a4c464b9323cfe121df4aeca6f23b3ecc","tid":706903,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"大坑東宣道小學有代課導師疑在堂上分享吸食大麻經驗，更展示煙草物體引起家長憂慮。該校今(18日)回應東網查詢表示，校方本月1日從學生口中獲悉由外判機構協辦的課後支援班代課導師，在課堂中與學生談論與毒品有關的話題，並展示類似煙草之物。 <br />\n<br />\n校方指高度重視事件，並關注對學生造成的影響，因此一直與警方緊密聯繫，作出跟進，現階段不便披露任何資料細節。校方就上述事件作跟進後，已在上周二(12日)向家長發放通告交代事件。"},{"pid":"744be045b69182167c39789ddef82167fa52b439","tid":706903,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49af9d7ec4e9efd3f2ddc95a9ba19ce511290e4","tid":706903,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:39:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67c228a75e9691e9b7989821b7727f9275e3eed0","tid":706903,"uid":28195,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"大麻合法化，學生自殺率跌至零"},{"pid":"d15c64561017b6f4f17dba874bd32c837d256ef5","tid":706903,"uid":80814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"深耕細作<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683d1e4574357268f0c42817132ac8234d4dfe07","tid":706903,"uid":26329,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"其實好老師黎 想學生真正學習 而唔係死讀書"},{"pid":"df140fbedb0fbc85d87c8794d121003cd0720d7c","tid":706903,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:57:45.000Z","msg":"睇下分享吸食大麻邊方面啦，講下吸食後壞處叫班學生唔好試咪ok囉"},{"pid":"656affc276d5514fecf38cf5a238f5f95380c680","tid":706903,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"cls 當年上BIO MISS都拎condom實物嚟教書啦<img src=